<body>
<h2>What's New in 1.7.3</h2>  <ul><li><strong>⌘R to refresh</strong> — press Command+R while the popover is open to instantly refresh both services</li> <li><strong>Rate limit handling</strong> — HTTP 429 responses are now surfaced as a clear "rate limited" message instead of a generic error</li> <li><strong>Fewer false network banners</strong> — the "No network connection" alert now only appears for genuine connectivity loss, not transient server or SSL errors</li> <li><strong>More breathing room</strong> — added spacing above the gauge rings</li></ul>
</body>
